@freezing-out, your perspective is also valuable. It's crucial to acknowledge the differences between various cultures, while also being mindful of the potential impact on others, especially children.

Let's keep the conversation going, focusing on understanding and learning from each other's viewpoints. Let's also remember to be considerate of the diverse backgrounds and experiences of our community members."

